p: The title compound was obtained in 40% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ 3.90 (s, 3H), 4.63 (s, 2H), 6.53 (d, J = 0.6 Hz, 1H), 6.55 (dd, J = 1.8, 3.3 Hz, 1H), 6.85 (d, J = 3.3 Hz, 1H), 7.10 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.31 (t, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.50 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 2H), 7.57 (d, J = 1.5 Hz, 1H), 8.01 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 2H), 8.30 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H), 9.04 (d, J = 2.1 Hz, 1H).
